x\"><span><font style=\"font-size: 14px\"><strong>【精湛工艺】采用传统钢琴制作工艺与现代科技结合的精湛工艺，在高档钢琴生产线上生产。</strong></font></span></span></p>\r\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(47,95,161); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(242,248,255); text-indent: 0px\"><span style=\"white-space: nowrap; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: left; orphans: 2; widows: 2; display: inline; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 5px\"><span><font style=\"font-size: 14px\"><strong>【不等厚音板】运用欧洲独特技术设计的不等厚音板，最符合钢琴共鸣系统的发声规律，使音色丰满圆润，柔和纯美。</strong></font></span></span></p>\r\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(47,95,161); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(242,248,255); text-indent: 0px\"><span style=\"white-space: nowrap; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: left; orphans: 2; widows: 2; display: inline; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 5px\"><span><font style=\"font-size: 14px\"><strong>【压弯弦码】弯压式的弦码，音频振动迅速、精准，音色纯正。</strong></font></span></span></p>\r\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(47,95,161); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(242,248,255); text-indent: 0px\"><span style=\"white-space: nowrap; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: left; orphans: 2; widows: 2; display: inline; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 5px\"><span><font style=\"font-size: 14px\"><strong>【击弦机】击弦机采用欧洲传统工艺制作，木制零件全部采用优质枫木，经特殊处理，不易变形，零件之间配合精准、运转灵敏。</strong></font></span></span></p>\r\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(47,95,161); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(242,248,255); text-indent: 0px\"><span style=\"white-space: nowrap; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: left; orphans: 2; widows: 2; display: inline; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 5px\"><span><font style=\"font-size: 14px\"><strong>【木材处理】采用电脑控制的全自动化大型木材干燥窑进行木材处理，关键部件的木材储备干燥超过3年以上，确保钢琴木制部件的稳定性。</strong></font></span></span></p>\r\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(47,95,161); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(242,248,255); text-indent: 0px\"><span style=\"white-space: nowrap; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: left; orphans: 2; widows: 2; display: inline; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 5px\"><span><font style=\"font-size: 14px\"><strong>【适应气候】核心部件的制作均经科学地设置含水率控制点和静止期，配套先进的工艺设施，使部件在任何气候环境下都保持稳定状态。</strong></font></span></span></p>\r\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(47,95,161); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(242,248,255); text-indent: 0px\"><span style=\"white-space: nowrap; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: left; orphans: 2; widows: 2; display: inline; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 5px\"><span><font style=\"font-size: 14px\"><strong>【制音毡】采用欧洲优质的毛毡制造，制音效果极佳。</strong></font></span></span></p>\r\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(47,95,161); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(242,248,255); text-indent: 0px\"><span style=\"white-space: nowrap; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: left; orphans: 2; widows: 2; display: inline; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 5px\"><span><font style=\"font-size: 14px\"><strong>【琴弦】采用德国ROSLAU琴弦，音色更出众。</strong></font></span></span></p>\r\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(47,95,161); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(242,248,255); text-indent: 0px\"><span style=\"white-space: nowrap; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: left; orphans: 2; widows: 2; display: inline; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 5px\"><span><font style=\"font-size: 14px\"><strong>【空调车间】在恒温恒湿的车间进行装配、音色整理和调音，保持稳</strong></font></span></span></p>\r\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(47,95,161); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(242,248,255); text-indent: 0px\"><span style=\"white-space: nowrap; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: left; orphans: 2; widows: 2; display: inline; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 5px\"><span><font style=\"font-size: 14px\"><strong>定的音准和弹奏性能。</strong></font></span></span></p>\r\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(47,95,161); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(242,248,255); text-indent: 0px\"><span style=\"white-space: nowrap; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: left; orphans: 2; widows: 2; display: inline; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 5px\"><span><font style=\"font-size: 14px\"><strong>【木黑键】名贵的乌木黑键，手感更舒适，观感高雅。</strong></font></span></span></p>\r\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(47,95,161); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(242,248,255); text-indent: 0px\"><span style=\"white-space: nowrap; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: left; orphans: 2; widows: 2; display: inline; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 5px\"><span><font style=\"font-size: 14px\"><strong>【缓降器】原装进口的键盖缓降器，持久耐用，安全舒适。</strong></font></span></span></p>\r\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(47,95,161); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(242,248,255); text-indent: 0px\"><span style=\"white-space: nowrap; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: left; orphans: 2; widows: 2; display: inline; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 5px\"><span><font style=\"font-size: 14px\"><strong>（请认准左键侧木上的珠江精品P系列钢琴标志</strong></font></span></span></p>\r\n    </li>\r\n</ul>', 'upimg/2015011712594482.jpg', '100', 'no', 'no', 'yes', '0', '59.41.205.216', '1421470791');
