m: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 12px/20px \'arial 宋体\'; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; border-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">德国罗斯劳琴弦和绕铜低音琴弦使音色更出众。</p>\r\n<p style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; white-space: normal; border-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(102,102,102); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 12px/20px \'arial 宋体\'; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; border-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; white-space: normal; border-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(102,102,102); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 12px/20px \'arial 宋体\'; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; border-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">【乌木黑键】</p>\r\n<p style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; white-space: normal; border-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(102,102,102); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 12px/20px \'arial 宋体\'; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; border-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; white-space: normal; border-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(102,102,102); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 12px/20px \'arial 宋体\'; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; border-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">精选名贵的乌木制造，手感舒适自然，外观高雅。</p>\r\n<p style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; white-space: normal; border-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(102,102,102); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 12px/20px \'arial 宋体\'; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; border-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; white-space: normal; border-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(102,102,102); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 12px/20px \'arial 宋体\'; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; border-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">【弦槌】</p>\r\n<p style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; white-space: normal; border-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(102,102,102); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 12px/20px \'arial 宋体\'; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; border-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; white-space: normal; border-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(102,102,102); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 12px/20px \'arial 宋体\'; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; border-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">使用德国雷诺牌（Louis Renner）弦槌,弹性硬度巧妙结合,带来完美音色。</p>\r\n<p style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; white-space: normal; border-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(102,102,102); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 12px/20px \'arial 宋体\'; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; border-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; white-space: normal; border-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(102,102,102); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 12px/20px \'arial 宋体\'; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; border-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">【击弦系统】</p>\r\n<p style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; white-space: normal; border-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(102,102,102); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 12px/20px \'arial 宋体\'; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; border-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; white-space: normal; border-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(102,102,102); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 12px/20px \'arial 宋体\'; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; border-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">精心设计的击弦系统，采用优质木材并由数控设备加工装配而成，状态稳定、反应灵敏精确。合金硬铝制造的击弦系统总档，提供稳定的装配基础，并使整理状态保持稳定。</p>\r\n<p style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; white-space: normal; border-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(102,102,102); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 12px/20px \'arial 宋体\'; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; border-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; white-space: normal; border-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(102,102,102); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 12px/20px \'arial 宋体\'; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; border-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">【生产线】</p>\r\n<p style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; white-space: normal; border-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(102,102,102); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 12px/20px \'arial 宋体\'; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; border-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; white-space: normal; border-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(102,102,102); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 12px/20px \'arial 宋体\'; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; border-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">恒温、恒湿的木装、总装生产车间，提高了恺撒堡系列钢琴的音准及弹奏性能的稳定性。</p>', 'upimg/2015011716112995.jpg', '100', 'no', 'no', 'yes', '0', '59.41.205.216', '1421482303');
