text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt\">录音功能：强大电脑程序录音播放系统,录音、回放，单曲最大12,000音符；</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt\">MIDI计算机状态录音支持64轨16通道、MIDI&nbsp;0&amp;1格式文件存储。</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left; text-transform: none; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 0px; font: 20px/24px 宋体; white-space: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(53,53,53); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt\">音色控制：三角大钢琴音色，双音色、双键盘，双键盘功能可调分离点；</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-transform: none; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 0px; font: 20px/24px 宋体; white-space: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(53,53,53); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt\">双音色：钢琴演奏带弦乐背景音色，用户可编辑多种组合音色。</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-transform: none; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 0px; font: 20px/24px 宋体; white-space: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(53,53,53); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt\">键盘分离：双钢琴，同音域，</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt\">可将键盘分割成两种相同音高的音区功能</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt\">、四手联弹、弦乐重奏、管乐合奏、钢琴+提琴，吉他+提琴演奏，可以实现多重组合。</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left; text-transform: none; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 0px; font: 20px/24px 宋体; white-space: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(53,53,53); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt\">音量控制：主音量，夜间弹奏可调节音量控制，夜间免打扰弹奏双接口；</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left; text-transform: none; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 0px; font: 20px/24px 宋体; white-space: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(53,53,53); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt\">移调：25档位，（0，-/+12）；</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left; text-transform: none; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 0px; font: 20px/24px 宋体; white-space: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(53,53,53); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt\">效果功能：64级深度混响、64级深度合唱；</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left; text-transform: none; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 0px; font: 20px/24px 宋体; white-space: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(53,53,53); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt\">节拍器：根据节拍发出强弱滴答声，1,2,3,4,5,6,7,8,9；</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left; text-transform: none; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 0px; font: 20px/24px 宋体; white-space: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(53,53,53); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt\">踏板功能：仿传统大三角钢琴踏板功能，可实现弱音踏板、选择延音踏板、延音踏板功能；</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left; text-transform: none; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 0px; font: 20px/24px 宋体; white-space: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(53,53,53); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt\">USB接口：USB&nbsp;MIDI计算机接口，可实现无限量歌曲录音存储，支持64轨16通道MIDI录音、支持MIDI&nbsp;0&amp;1格式文件，GM国际标准，还可实现系统的无限扩展和升级；</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left; text-transform: none; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 0px; font: 20px/24px 宋体; white-space: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(53,53,53); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt\">音频播放器：U盘接口，SD卡接口，蓝牙接驳器，可以支持安卓或苹果系统手机或者IPAD播放MP3音频文件的音乐。</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left; text-transform: none; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 0px; font: 20px/24px 宋体; white-space: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(53,53,53); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt\">接口：USB接口，MIDI&nbsp;IN/OUT接口，踏板接口,电源接口,耳机插孔*2，立体声线路输入(*2)/输出(*2)；</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-transform: none; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: -21pt; font: 20px/24px 宋体; white-space: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(53,53,53); margin-left: 21pt; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt\">音响系统：</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt\">意大利音响设计大师Max设计</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt\">独立音箱带导向管专业二分频技术四喇叭环绕立体</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-transform: none; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: -21pt; font: 20px/24px 宋体; white-space: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(53,53,53); margin-left: 21pt; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt\">声高级音响系统，</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt\">高频与中低频分箱体独立置放增强声音层次感，顶球丝膜高音提供圆润清</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-transform: none; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: -21pt; font: 20px/24px 宋体; white-space: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(53,53,53); margin-left: 21pt; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt\">晰高频，重低音衍射提供良好的声音成像，1寸厚度木质外壳材料有效消除共振，音频超指</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-transform: none; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: -21pt; font: 20px/24px 宋体; white-space: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(53,53,53); margin-left: 21pt; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt\">向性控制波导技术演奏华彩乐章，准确的声像定位和连续的声像群分布与出色的频率均衡，</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-transform: none; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: -21pt; font: 20px/24px 宋体; white-space: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(53,53,53); margin-left: 21pt; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt\">房间响应修正控制能保证音响在任何声学环境下的最佳工作状态。</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-transform: none; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 0px; font: 20px/24px 宋体; white-space: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(53,53,53); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt\">三角大钢琴：达到传统九尺大三角钢琴音色效果，实现演奏家音乐厅演奏效果。</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left; text-transform: none; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 0px; font: 20px/24px 宋体; white-space: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(53,53,53); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt\">MIDI键盘:通过USB与计算机连接可以实现编曲配器，方便作曲工作者的需求。</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left; text-transform: none; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 0px; font: 20px/24px 宋体; white-space: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(53,53,53); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt\">GM标准音源：通过USB与计算机连接的MIDI状态下可以实现GM标准音源的应用效果。</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-transform: none; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: -63pt; font: 20px/24px 宋体; white-space: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(53,53,53); margin-left: 63pt; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt\">有源音箱：可支持MP3/MP4/DVD/PC机/SAMSUNG等连接或蓝牙音频载入。</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-transform: none; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: -21pt; font: 20px/24px 宋体; white-space: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(53,53,53); margin-left: 21pt; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt\">吉他音箱：</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt\">可支持电箱吉他的音响放大器功能，吉他手的音响大师。</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left; text-transform: none; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 0px; font: 20px/24px 宋体; white-space: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(53,53,53); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt\">功率：80W（二分频四喇叭环绕立体声）；电压：交流220V；</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left; text-transform: none; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 0px; font: 20px/24px 宋体; white-space: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(53,53,53); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt\">尺寸：1355*340*750（mm，</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 10.5pt\">长*宽*高</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt\">）；净重量：45kg；</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left; text-transform: none; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 0px; font: 20px/24px 宋体; white-space: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(53,53,53); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt\">配件：电源线，保修卡，合格证书，使用说明书。</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left; text-transform: none; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 0px; font: 20px/24px 宋体; white-space: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(53,53,53); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left; text-transform: none; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 0px; font: 20px/24px 宋体; white-space: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(53,53,53); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold\">更多优点：</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left; text-transform: none; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 0px; font: 20px/24px 宋体; white-space: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(53,53,53); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt\">1.</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt\">配送珠江艾茉森智能教学数码钢琴视频五线谱软件。</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left; text-transform: none; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 0px; font: 20px/24px 宋体; white-space: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(53,53,53); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt\">2.</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt\">通过USB与笔记本电脑连接即可实现有声视频五线谱音乐教材教学。</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left; text-transform: none; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 0px; font: 20px/24px 宋体; white-space: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(53,53,53); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt\">3.</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt\">连接无线话筒即可实现卡拉OK、自弹自唱功能。</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left; text-transform: none; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 0px; font: 20px/24px 宋体; white-space: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(53,53,53); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt\">4.</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt\">通过蓝牙即可实现手机对接唱吧WAV录音，歌词伴奏同步、微信微博分享。</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left; text-transform: none; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 0px; font: 20px/24px 宋体; white-space: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(53,53,53); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt\">5.</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt\">大谱架，可以实现两本书以上的放置。</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left; text-transform: none; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 0px; font: 20px/24px 宋体; white-space: normal; margin-bottom: 0pt; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(53,53,53); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt\">6.</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt\">键盖折叠书桌设计，放下时可以作为写字书桌使用。</span></div>', 'upimg/2015042415295981.jpg', '41', 'no', 'no', 'yes', '0', '59.41.99.97', '1429860647');
