ll\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><strong>键盘分离：</strong>双钢琴，同音域可将键盘分割成两种相同的音高的音区功能、四手联</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 13px/23px 瀹嬩綋; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: small\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">&nbsp;&nbsp; 弹、弦乐重奏、管乐合奏、钢琴+提琴，吉他+提琴演奏，可以实现多重组合。</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 13px/23px 瀹嬩綋; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: small\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><strong>音量控制：</strong>主音量，夜间弹奏可调节音量控制，夜间免打扰弹奏双接口；</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 13px/23px 瀹嬩綋; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: small\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><strong>移调：</strong>25档位，（0，-/+12）；</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 13px/23px 瀹嬩綋; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: small\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><strong>效果功能：</strong>8级深度混响、8级深度合唱；</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 13px/23px 瀹嬩綋; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: small\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><strong>节拍器：</strong>根据节拍发出强弱滴答声，1,2,3,4,5,6；</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 13px/23px 瀹嬩綋; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: small\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><strong>USB接口：</strong>USB MIDI计算机接口，可实现无限量歌曲录音存储，MIDI键盘功能，</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 13px/23px 瀹嬩綋; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: small\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">&nbsp;&nbsp; 编曲配器，GM标准音源，实现系统的无限扩展和升级系统；</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 13px/23px 瀹嬩綋; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: small\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><strong>接口：</strong>踏板接口,电源接口,耳机插孔，立体声线路输入/输出 。</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 13px/23px 瀹嬩綋; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: small\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><strong>踏板功能：</strong>弱音踏板，制音踏板，延音踏板，仿传统大三角钢琴踏板功能；</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 13px/23px 瀹嬩綋; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: small\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><strong>音响系统：</strong>意大利技术设计立体声双喇叭音响系统。</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 13px/23px 瀹嬩綋; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: small\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><strong>电源:</strong><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>DC12V/2000mA;</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 13px/23px 瀹嬩綋; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: small\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><strong>尺寸:</strong><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>137 *&nbsp;43&nbsp;* 102 （长*宽*高，cm）</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 13px/23px 瀹嬩綋; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: small\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><strong>重量：</strong>52 KG</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 13px/23px 瀹嬩綋; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: small\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><strong>配件:</strong><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>电源适配器，保修卡，合格证书，使用说明书。</span></span></p>', 'upimg/2015042415380972.jpg', '43', 'no', 'no', 'yes', '0', '59.41.99.97', '1429861094');
