text-transform: none; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 12px/18px arial, 宋体; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(102,102,102); border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0,0,0); padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-size: 18px; padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 27px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">恺撒堡</span><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 27px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">KN</span><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 27px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">梦幻</span><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 27px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">系列立式钢琴</span><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 27px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">共有</span><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 27px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">4</span><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 27px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">个型号，包括</span><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 27px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">KN1</span><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 27px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">、</span><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 27px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">KN2</span><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 27px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">、</span><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 27px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">KN3</span><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 27px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">和</span><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 27px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">KN6</span><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 27px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">。</span><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 27px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">外观以家族化的设计思路，线条优雅的弧形琴身，凸显欧洲本真的精湛工艺。</span></span></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 12px/18px arial, 宋体; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(102,102,102); border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0,0,0); padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-size: 18px; padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 27px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">上门突破立式琴的设计局限，采用全新的双透音孔设计，使全音域得到扩展，琴声清晰入耳，音色更为细腻动听，大幅提升音色效果。</span></span></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 12px/18px arial, 宋体; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(102,102,102); border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 12px/18px arial, 宋体; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(102,102,102); border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0,0,0); padding-top: 0px\"><b style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 27px; text-indent: 24.1pt; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-size: 18px; padding-top: 0px\">【技术工艺和配置亮点】</b></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 12px/18px arial, 宋体; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(102,102,102); border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0,0,0); padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-size: 18px; padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 27px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">恺撒堡</span><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 27px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">KN</span><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 27px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">梦幻</span><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 27px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">系列立式钢琴</span><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 27px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">采用了弦列不和谐系数设计技术、音板振动模态分析技术、音板框拟合曲面设计、不等厚音板设计、弯压结构弦码、加强型背柱不对称分布等先进设计技术，并配置了进口鱼鳞松音板、德国雷诺弦槌、乌木（檀木）黑键等优质材料。</span><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 27px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">各个型号均</span><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 27px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">安装优质键盖缓降器。</span></span></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 12px/18px arial, 宋体; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(102,102,102); border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 12px/18px arial, 宋体; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(102,102,102); border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0,0,0); padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-size: 18px; padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 27px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">该系列钢琴的共鸣系统运用最新研制的、达到国际领先水平的共鸣系统数控加工设备进行制作，零部件加工精度大幅提升，共鸣效果更佳，音色更完美。</span></span></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 12px/18px arial, 宋体; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(102,102,102); border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0,0,0); padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-size: 18px; padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 27px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">为增加产品的档次和视觉效果，采用最新研制的金葱粉铁板涂饰工艺，凸显铁板的金属质感，闪金的颜色效果提高了产品的档次，并配以相同涂饰的新型框架式弱音档，使产品更具欧式风格。<img width=\"800\" height=\"672\" alt=\"\" src=\"/stsm/edit_file/image/20150427/2015042716045310.jpg\" /></span></span></span></span></div>', 'upimg/2015042716025694.jpg', '100', 'no', 'no', 'yes', '0', '59.41.36.116', '1430121777');
