right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 27px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">上门突破立式琴的设计局限，采用全新的双透音孔设计，使全音域得到扩展，琴声清晰入耳，音色更为细腻动听，大幅提升音色效果。</span></span></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 12px/18px arial, 宋体; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(102,102,102); border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 12px/18px arial, 宋体; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(102,102,102); border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0,0,0); padding-top: 0px\"><b style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 27px; text-indent: 24.1pt; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-size: 18px; padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 27px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">【技术工艺和配置亮点】</span></b></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 12px/18px arial, 宋体; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(102,102,102); border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0,0,0); padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; paddi